query:
SELECT c.id as cycleId, c.title as cycleTitle, w.id as weekId, w.weekGroup, w.title as weekTitle
FROM cycles c
JOIN weeks w ON w.cycleId = c.id
WHERE w.type = 'live' AND c.`order` BETWEEN 1 AND 6
ORDER BY c.`order`, w.weekGroup;
